      <h2
        style="font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
        <i class="bi bi-phone-vibrate" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #28a745;"></i> Explore o App AquaPulse
